# Deploy project: frontend/backend and port conventions

Use the following rules when editing the deploy repo or when adding or designing apps that will be added to it:

- **deploy-service-naming.mdc** — Service naming (`<project>-backend`, `<project>-frontend`, etc.) and port convention (8080 / 80).
- **deploy-ghcr-images.mdc** — GHCR image naming and `.env.prod` image variables.
- **deploy-add-new-project.mdc** — Step-by-step checklist for adding a new project (compose, Caddyfile, scripts, config).
- **deploy-app-integration.mdc** — Requirements for app projects that will join deploy (ports, image names).
